# GIFs Directory

This directory contains animated GIFs demonstrating key features.

## Guidelines

- Follow the GIF specifications in DEMO_GUIDE.md
- Keep file sizes small (< 5MB)
- Use 10-15 FPS for smooth playback
- Duration: 3-10 seconds

## Required GIFs

- command-translation.gif - Command translation process
- command-execution.gif - Command execution process
- history-search.gif - History search functionality
- template-usage.gif - Template usage workflow
- theme-toggle.gif - Theme switching animation
- responsive-layout.gif - Responsive layout demonstration

## Optimization

Use tools like gifsicle or gifski to optimize GIF files:

```bash
gifsicle -O3 --colors 256 input.gif -o output.gif
```
